                    button.btn.btn-secondary(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#' + name, aria-expanded='false', aria-controls=name)
                        span.caret
            span.form-text.text-muted Click to copy

        include _partials/jscode.pug

    hr.my-4

    .card.border-info
        .card-header.bg-info.text-white
            h3.card-title Info
        .card-body
            | Bootstrap 4 is currently in Beta release and should be treated as such. For details check out 
            a(href='https://blog.getbootstrap.com/2017/08/10/bootstrap-4-beta/', target='_blank', rel='noopener').
                the Bootstrap 4 Beta announcement
            | .

    h3.text-center.mt-4='v' + config.bootstrap4[0].version

